data.description: Beautiful, updated, 3 bed 2 bath pool home with gorgeous water view in highly desirable Coral Springs neighborhood w/ NO HOA. Kitchen completely remodeled (2022) features quartz countertops, soft close cabinets & drawers w/ pullouts, recessed lighting & stainless-steel appliances. Tile roof 2016. AC 2018. Hot water heater 2020. Washer & Dyer 2023. Gigantic pool w/ new surface & pavers (2023). The large fully fenced backyard overlooks the canal & park. Irrigation system. Huge Florida Room w/AC. Tile & laminate floors throughout. Primary bedroom has big walk-in closet. Guest bathroom is remodeled w/ vanity & tiled shower. Textured ceilings throughout (No Popcorn). Oversized garage with newer impact garage door. Accordion shutters & Panels. Large stamped concrete driveway. Great location!
